{"tid":2190814,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(將太末日) 壽司郎用漫畫宣傳機器壽司、侮辱傳統日本料理","createTime":"2020-09-06T03:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T07:35:32.000Z","uid":223256,"like":2,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"03f58b1943103af16b5ca01c5730fdab15a71147","tid":2190814,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"尋日口痕去食壽司郎、見到舖頭大大張海報宣傳個(新漫畫)<br />\n壽司路 (Sushiroad)<br />\n屌你老母咁似將太的壽司既?<br />\n原來真係搵寺尺大介畫既<br />\n宣傳: 有熱血、背叛一身既壽司之路<br />\n<br />\n漫畫連結<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.akindo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akindo&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=2854fdd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.akindo</a>-sushir<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdOF8VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdOF8VE.jpg&h=c4b7a05a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://o.co.jp/sushiroad/tw/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fo.co.jp%2Fsushiroad%2Ftw%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=57706af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">o.co.jp/sushiroad/tw/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心諗、寺尺又有壽司漫畫新提材?<br />\n唔睇由自可、睇完真係把鬼火<br />\n自此決定<br />\n以後唔食壽司郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"d425a6d0087f74a3bf2f3d938458f6d9e672f972","tid":2190814,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.akindo-sushiro.co.jp/sushiroad/tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akindo-sushiro.co.jp%2Fsushiroad%2Ftw%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=64604f36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.akindo-sushiro.co.jp/sushiroad/tw/</a><br />\n<br />\n補返連結先"},{"pid":"08ee4826c738f2d4f629b3fc7bca76b44a24c4df","tid":2190814,"uid":223256,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSf5AE9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSf5AE9.jpg&h=7733f162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZ6sO0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZ6sO0a.jpg&h=9f26179d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你咁多似將太的壽司裡面個佐治安人既? 仲講到佢地想一鑊玩起達角(壽司狼)? 有無咁撚卑鄙呀?<br />\n<br />\n主角因為無晒壽司師父煩惱緊<br />\n結果出左個工程師話要幫佢<br />\n<br />\n仆街狐狸的尾巴終於出現了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ltr4Req.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtr4Req.jpg&h=df92e073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c30pRer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc30pRer.jpg&h=b0daff4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SX2onk7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSX2onk7.jpg&h=f8730539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wdrj7O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wdrj7O.jpg&h=668b2056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Yw0809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Yw0809.jpg&h=bb398101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講<br />\n裡面跟本唔係漫畫<br />\n而係用漫畫手法去幫舖頭用機器整壽司飯去洗底<br />\n咁你講乜春比人背叛呢?<br />\n真果間壽司郎幾時比人玩野集體辭職呀?<br />\n有既話、拿出證據來<br />\n我即刻道歉加賠償<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實壽司郎用機器整壽司飯唔係新鮮事<br />\n我唔反對佢地咁做<br />\n成本效益、加上要快、無可厚非<br />\n但呢張圖堅離譜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLPYVHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLPYVHF.jpg&h=868fa859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQRP2nJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQRP2nJ.jpg&h=7df44026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbdaad1e13c5cd5244422cb9dcb4ca048531b0d3","tid":2190814,"uid":351030,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"你係咪元氣 爭鮮 既人？"},{"pid":"066f4f5d0a2818864c9792a647f8ebc5cb155e83","tid":2190814,"uid":74163,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"你唔食大把人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e02b862a74af583f5941e7ccbf78b73cae86a07","tid":2190814,"uid":65933,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c660291e11a81d29be9c5253946184ba355210","tid":2190814,"uid":46943,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"唔好用雪櫃囉<br />\n機器黎"},{"pid":"9431ef5a1c890c2f5f7c2f4048959c7981d5accb","tid":2190814,"uid":223256,"like":4,"dislike":43,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"4e02b862a74af583f5941e7ccbf78b73cae86a07","tid":2190814,"uid":65933,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"你用機器整壽司無問題<br />\n你用漫畫方法都無問題<br />\n但你用(漫畫情節)講到壽司郎比人迫害<br />\n焗住用機器整壽司就大有問題<br />\n因為現實無人迫害壽司郎<br />\n只係因為經營原因咁做<br />\n你仲要話機器整得好食過人手<br />\n你唔係侮辱傳統壽司店係乜?<br />\n<br />\n爭鮮同元氣都會用機器<br />\n無人會怪壽司郎你都用<br />\n但你搵將太的壽司司個作者去老作劇情係合理發機器壽司就係卑鄙行為<br />\n點解唔光明正大去宣傳?<br />\n要用下三流既手段?<br />\n你唔止整臭壽司郎<br />\n仲整臭埋寺尺大介呀屌你<br />\n<br />\n將太的壽司幾時有講過機器好過人手呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"888e3f5c16de501e23ecc4bc9138b148e23bda49","tid":2190814,"uid":47478,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"原來只係個睇漫畫睇到上曬腦嘅中二毒撚開post"},{"pid":"61f176443f1246df237a6a4a7c64c12e6e299c3d","tid":2190814,"uid":65933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9431ef5a1c890c2f5f7c2f4048959c7981d5accb","tid":2190814,"uid":223256,"like":4,"